gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3512e1f7ab1dac59b46ca66f76d2eb1178fef7fe","tid":1613810,"uid":292925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:28:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">搞Starbuck=自取滅亡</span></span><br />\n香港求緊美國幫手但係自己去打爆人地D野, 想點?冇撚病啊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">外國人唔會理亦都唔會花時間了解Starbucks同美心關係</span><br />\n佢地只係見到平時最鍾重飲既Starbuck比Crazy Hong Kong people打爆哂<br />\nStarbuck Coffee對鬼佬黎講等於香港魚蛋燒買, 你地想像下香港小食檔比外國人打爆哂你有咩感受?<br />\n香港人一直都係做緊「被害者」呢個角色先會比國際同情,支持<br />\n宜家人地會覺得香港人變左「施暴者」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人開始殺鬼佬啦!好恐怖呀!</span><br />\n<br />\n認真想問點解呢D全部冇事:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中資Pacific Coffee<br />\n中資華潤超市<br />\n奶共張敬軒 空中酒吧 The Crown<br />\n奶共余文樂 華嫂冰室 </span><br />\n <br />\n咁多野唔搞係都要搞9美國野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a471de7e8e4523708be15a146b2007098ed4bd","tid":1613810,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T23:50:19.000Z","msg":"Starbucks 的文宣,建議用英文"},{"pid":"ebd500f76843139e12732f4d81aec74a89c05bfc","tid":1613810,"uid":45305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:54:59.000Z","msg":"希望大家肯睇下"},{"pid":"350a44ba601710baa35dac640da460e818aaf9c7","tid":1613810,"uid":36915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:55:48.000Z","msg":"你都on9"}]}